			<h1>
				<a href="http://werblog.com/2006/04/we-want-freedom/" title="We Want Freedom!" rel="bookmark">We Want Freedom!</a>
				<i class="comment-bubble">1</i>
			</h1>

			<div class="post-footer">
				3 Apr 2006 &nbsp;&nbsp;| <a href="http://werblog.com/category/uncategorized/">Uncategorized</a>
				
			</div>

			<div class="post-bodycopy cf">
				<p>I wasn&#8217;t able to make it to my friend David Isenberg&#8217;s <a href="http://freedom-to-connect.net/">Freedom to Connect</a> conference  this year, but I&#8217;m sure it will be a fantastic discussion of telecom policy and the future of the Net.  David is now partnering with my other friend Jeff Pulver to organize the event; live streaming audio is available <a href="http://freedom-to-connect.net/stream.html">here</a>.</p>

				
			</div>

			
			


